{"type": "root", "attrs": {"type": "node", "context": "sop", "icon": "SHELF/wave", "internal": "oceanwaves", "since": "16.0", "version": null, "namespace": null}, "body": [{"level": 0, "type": "title", "indent": 0, "text": ["Ocean Waves"], "extent": [0, 16]}, {"type": "summary", "indent": 0, "text": ["Instances individual waveforms onto input points and generated points."], "extent": [97, 175]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This node creates an ocean layer comprised of waveforms instanced onto input points and / or points generated within this SOP to create a wave train.  The output of this node can be merged with other ocean layers created by this node or the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/oceanspectrum", "type": "link", "text": ["Ocean Spectrum SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/oceanspectrum"}, "."], "extent": [175, 462]}, {"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["If points are plugged into the first input of this node, waveforms will be instanced onto each input point with position and orientation controlled by its ", {"scheme": null, "value": "/copy/instanceattrs", "type": "link", "text": ["Copying and Instancing"], "fullpath": "/copy/instanceattrs"}, " attributes and the randomized parameters on the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Shape"]}, " tab of this node.   This node can also generate its own instance points using the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Waves"]}, " section.  The second input can be a volume mask similar to the one input to the ", {"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/oceanspectrum", "type": "link", "text": ["Ocean Spectrum SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/oceanspectrum"}, "."], "extent": [462, 938]}, {"level": 1, "id": "parameters", "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [938, 950], "body": [{"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Waves"], "extent": [950, 963], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 0, "text": ["This section controls internally generated wave points."], "extent": [963, 1021]}, {"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Number of Waves"], "extent": [1021, 1038], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The number of wavefronts to create."], "extent": [1038, 1079]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Points Per Wave"], "extent": [1079, 1096], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The number of points in each wave.  Each point will have a small waveform of the specified ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Radius"]}, " instanced onto it to create a waveform."], "extent": [1096, 1243]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Size"], "extent": [1243, 1249], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The overall size across of the wave."], "extent": [1249, 1291]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Separation"], "extent": [1291, 1303], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The distance between each wavefront if ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Number of Waves"]}, " is greater than 1."], "extent": [1303, 1386]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Direction"], "extent": [1386, 1397], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The general direction the wavefronts will be facing.  This can be overridden on a per-point basis with the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Rotation"]}, " point parameter."], "extent": [1397, 1539]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Jitter Seed"], "extent": [1539, 1552], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The random seed used in jittering the wave points."], "extent": [1552, 1608]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Jitter Scale"], "extent": [1608, 1622], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The amount to jitter the generated wave points in the ZX plane."], "extent": [1622, 1691]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Animation Type"], "extent": [1691, 1707], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The method used for animating the waves.  ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Wave Speed"]}, " will move the wave in the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Direction"]}, " they are pointing by the specified ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Speed"]}, ".  ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Center"]}, " will move the center of the wavetrain."], "extent": [1707, 1906]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Speed"], "extent": [1906, 1913], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The speed at which the waves should move."], "extent": [1913, 1960]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Offset"], "extent": [1960, 1968], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The amount to offset the wave train along the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Direction"]}, " vector."], "extent": [1968, 2041]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Center"], "extent": [2041, 2049], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The center of the wave train.    "], "extent": [2049, 2088]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}, {"level": 2, "id": null, "container": true, "type": "h", "indent": 0, "text": ["Shape"], "extent": [2088, 2100], "body": [{"type": "parameters_item_group", "body": [{"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Crest Width"], "extent": [2100, 2114], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The width of each individual waveform."], "extent": [2114, 2158]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Chop"], "extent": [2158, 2164], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The amount of sharp cusps the waves will have.  Increasing this value too high can cause the waves to become too peaked and invert on themselves."], "extent": [2164, 2315]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Radius"], "extent": [2315, 2323], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The radius of the instanced wave area.  This parameter overwrites any incoming ", {"type": "code", "text": ["pscale"]}, " attribute on the input points."], "extent": [2323, 2447]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Variance"], "extent": [2447, 2457], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The amount of randomness in the instanced ocean radius."], "extent": [2478, 2539]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "pointradvar"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Rotation"], "extent": [2539, 2549], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The amount to rotate the instanced waves.  This parameter overwrites any incoming ", {"type": "code", "text": ["rot"]}, " attribute on the input points."], "extent": [2549, 2673]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Variance"], "extent": [2673, 2683], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The amount of randomness in the instanced ocean orientation."], "extent": [2704, 2770]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "pointrotvar"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Amplitude"], "extent": [2770, 2781], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["An amplitude scaling for the instanced waves.  This parameter overwrites any incoming ", {"type": "code", "text": ["amplitude"]}, " attribute on the input points."], "extent": [2781, 2915]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Variance"], "extent": [2915, 2925], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The amount of randomness in the instanced ocean orientation."], "extent": [2946, 3012]}], "container": true, "attrs": {"id": "pointampvar"}, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Shape Seed"], "extent": [3012, 3024], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["A random seed for the ", {"type": "ui", "text": ["Shape"]}, " parameters."], "extent": [3024, 3074]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}, {"type": "parameters_item", "indent": 0, "text": ["Compute Velocity"], "extent": [3074, 3092], "body": [{"type": "para", "indent": 4, "text": ["The method used for computing point velocities.  The wave instancing points should have proper point velocities to ensure correctly calculated ocean velocities."], "extent": [3092, 3258]}], "container": true, "role": "item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group"}]}], "text": "Parameters"}, {"level": 1, "id": "related", "container": true, "type": "related_section", "indent": 0, "role": "section", "extent": [3258, 3267], "body": [{"type": "bullet_group", "body": [{"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/oceanspectrum", "type": "link", "text": ["Ocean Spectrum"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/oceanspectrum"}], "extent": [3267, 3310]}, {"blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "indent": 0, "text": [{"scheme": "Node", "value": "/nodes/sop/oceanevaluate", "type": "link", "text": ["Ocean Evaluate"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/oceanevaluate"}], "extent": [3310, 3352]}], "container": true}], "text": "Related"}], "title": ["Ocean Waves"], "summary": ["Instances individual waveforms onto input points and generated points."]}